 single point of failure.\n5-min publish SLA violated immediately.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bd5","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Transcode queue outpaces worker pool.\nPostgreSQL job table full-scan at scale.\nAPI server OOM from upload buffer growth.\nSingle DB is a hard single point of failure.\n5-min publish SLA violated immediately.","height":81.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#E2E4ED","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1156598396,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":2118.1204674799592,"angle":0,"y":-7476.6798051287624,"width":279.3306884765625},{"seed":1017152196,"strokeStyle":"dashed","id":"C5fueMPcdHwFhUPokQENt","strokeWidth":1,"roughness":0,"isDeleted":false,"startBinding":null,"endArrowhead":null,"opacity":100,"updated":1772895686408,"locked":false,"points":[[0,0],[0,840]],"polygon":false,"version":5,"type":"line","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bd6","roundness":null,"lastCommittedPoint":null,"height":840,"link":null,"startArrowhead":null,"strokeColor":"#2A2D3A","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"endBinding":null,"versionNonce":2028776260,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":3568.1204674799592,"angle":0,"y":-8154.6798051287624,"width":0},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#2A2D3A","link":null,"roughness":0,"groupIds":[],"index":"bd7","backgroundColor":"#1E2030","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"version":5,"roundness":null,"type":"rectangle","updated":1772895686408,"id":"W68aoPkAVspUuCWWQmmEC","x":3588.1204674799592,"seed":1854638660,"boundElements":[],"y":-8114.6798051287624,"opacity":100,"height":720,"width":860,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1509530364},{"seed":1286185412,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"T3AcWmKnJp-5h7OxbPSNt","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":18,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772895686408,"locked":false,"text":"Why Start Simple","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bd8","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Why Start Simple","height":22.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#E2E4ED","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":272540356,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":3604.1204674799592,"angle":0,"y":-8098.6798051287624,"width":148.62591552734375},{"seed":2115553604,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"PDuJlhoqtwJ6iyyAM5vXL","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772895686408,"locked":false,"text":"The baseline establishes what the system must do before\naddressing how to scale it. Six components are enough to ship:\na client, a monolith API, a job-queue-backed transcode worker\npool, one PostgreSQL database, object storage for durability,\nand a CDN for delivery. This can be built by a small team in\n6 weeks and comfortably serves hundreds of thousands of users\nwith zero distributed systems complexity.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bd9","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"The baseline establishes what the system must do before\naddressing how to scale it. Six components are enough to ship:\na client, a monolith API, a job-queue-backed transcode worker\npool, one PostgreSQL database, object storage for durability,\nand a CDN for delivery. This can be built by a small team in\n6 weeks and comfortably serves hundreds of thousands of users\nwith zero distributed systems complexity.","height":122.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#E2E4ED","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":310696828,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":3604.1204674799592,"angle":0,"y":-8070.6798051287624,"width":445.10140991210938},{"seed":372703428,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"Pl_VJxlcOw1hYoxn3vuZg","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":18,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772895686408,"locked":false,"text":"The Failure Cascade","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bdA","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"The Failure Cascade","height":22.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#E2E4ED","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1768270404,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":3604.1204674799592,"angle":0,"y":-7898.6798051287624,"width":177.55191040039062},{"seed":211961924,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"ZOFiqOIWAxpZJBZfcAyi1","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772895686408,"locked":false,"text":"Traffic crosses 1,000 concurrent uploads. The transcode worker\npool falls behind: each 1-hour video takes 30-60 min of CPU,\nso 50 simultaneous uploads saturate all cores. The pending_jobs\ntable grows to millions of rows. A polling query on status=pending\nwith no partial index degrades to a full table scan, spiking DB\nCPU to 100%. The API server connection pool exhausts waiting\nfor DB responses. Requests buffer in memory until the OS OOM-\nkills the API process. Zero uploads, logins, or playback: full outage.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bdB","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Traffic crosses 1,000 concurrent uploads. The transcode worker\npool falls behind: each 1-hour video takes 30-60 min of CPU,\nso 50 simultaneous uploads saturate all cores. The pending_jobs\ntable grows to millions of rows. A polling query on status=pending\nwith no partial index degrades to a full table scan, spiking DB\nCPU to 100%. The API server connection pool exhausts waiting\nfor DB responses. Requests buffer in memory until the OS OOM-\nkills the API process. Zero uploads, logins, or playback: full outage.","height":140,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#E2E4ED","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":148114428,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":3604.1204674799592,"angle":0,"y":-7870.6798051287624,"width":461.5513916015625},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#4D9E7C","link":null,"roughness":0,"groupIds":[],"index":"bdC","backgroundColor":"#252838","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772895686408,"id":"vGlVfrtx8wF_Dhp_Ge_T4","x":3592.1204674799592,"seed":892903364,"boundElements":[],"y":-7638.6798051287624,"opacity":100,"height":110,"width":852,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":658489796},{"seed":941098820,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"8ir0uETSHHSOjuV_59tGg","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772895686408,"locked":false,"text":"Key insight: The most fragile point is the PostgreSQL job queue\ntable — it couples upload rate, transcode capacity, and API health\ninto one table. Separating the job queue into a dedicated message\nbroker (Kafka\/SQS) is the first and highest-leverage fix.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bdD","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Key insight: The most fragile point is the PostgreSQL job queue\ntable — it couples upload rate, transcode capacity, and API health\ninto one table. Separating the job queue into a dedicated message\nbroker (Kafka\/SQS) is the first and highest-leverage fix.","height":70,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#9AA0B4","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1055468668,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":3608.1204674799592,"angle":0,"y":-7622.6798051287624,"width":459.28347778320312},{"seed":161382084,"strokeStyle":"dashed","id":"jpgVTk67tnRZeRZzYG48k","strok